com.joliciel.talismane.posTagger

Class PosTaggedToken

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.joliciel.talismane.tokeniser.TaggedToken<PosTag>
      • com.joliciel.talismane.posTagger.PosTaggedToken
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasFeatureCache, PosTaggedTokenWrapper, PosTaggerContext, TokenWrapper, Comparable<TaggedToken<PosTag>>

    public class PosTaggedToken
extends TaggedToken<PosTag>
implements PosTaggedTokenWrapper, HasFeatureCache, PosTaggerContext
    A token with a postag tagged onto it.
    Note: this class naturally implements PosTaggerContext since if a token has already been pos-tagged, the once before it have been pos-tagged as well. This allows us to use the same features on the token currently being pos-tagged and tokens already pos-tagged.
    Author:
    Assaf Urieli
